casebody.data:
Monique CASEY, petitioner,
v.
Sean CASEY. No. 12-8945. Supreme Court of the United States April 22, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until May, 13, 2013, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance *2017with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
